<div class="seatmap-workspace seatmap-workspace--stage3 stage3-workspace"
     id="stage3App"
     data-project-id="{{projectId}}"
     data-stage2-url="{{stage2Url}}"
     data-stage4-url="{{stage4Url}}"
     data-button-image-url="{{seatmapImageUrl}}">

    <aside class="seatmap-side seatmap-side--left stage3-left">
        <div class="stage3-title">
            <strong>Stage 03 · 구역 나누기</strong>
            <span>자동 추출한 구역을 A~Z 그룹으로 묶고, A1~An 번호만 확정합니다.</span>
        </div>

        <div class="stage3-step-list">
            <section class="stage3-step is-active" id="part1Panel" data-step="1">
                <button type="button" class="stage3-step__header active" id="partBtn1">
                    <span class="stage3-step__num">1</span>
                    <span class="stage3-step__text">
                        <b>구역 자동 나누기</b>
                        <small>button-image.png 연결 도형 분리</small>
                    </span>
                    <span class="stage3-step__status">진행중</span>
                </button>

                <div class="stage3-step__body">
                    <div class="stage3-card">
                        <p class="stage3-help">
                            색상 단색화가 끝난 이미지를 그대로 읽고, 서로 떨어진 도형 덩어리를 구역 후보로 만듭니다.
                            구역 안의 글자/구멍은 외곽 polygon 안에 포함된 것으로 보고 별도 좌석이나 버튼으로 처리하지 않습니다.
                        </p>

                        <div class="stage3-form-grid stage3-form-grid--two">
                            <div>
                                <label for="minArea">최소 구역 면적</label>
                                <input type="number" id="minArea" value="120" min="1">
                            </div>
                            <div>
                                <label for="bgTolerance">배경 허용범위</label>
                                <input type="number" id="bgTolerance" value="34" min="1" max="160">
                            </div>
                            <div>
                                <label for="simplifyTolerance">외곽 단순화</label>
                                <input type="number" id="simplifyTolerance" value="4" min="0" max="30">
                            </div>
                            <div>
                                <label for="snapSize">좌표 스냅</label>
                                <input type="number" id="snapSize" value="0" min="0" max="30">
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <button type="button" class="stage3-btn stage3-btn--primary" id="autoExtractBtn">구역 자동 나누기</button>
                        <button type="button" class="stage3-btn" id="clearSectionsBtn">구역 초기화</button>
                        <button type="button" class="stage3-btn stage3-btn--primary" id="goPart2Btn">다음: 그룹 수정</button>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>

            <section class="stage3-step" id="part2Panel" data-step="2">
                <button type="button" class="stage3-step__header" id="partBtn2">
                    <span class="stage3-step__num">2</span>
                    <span class="stage3-step__text">
                        <b>구역 선택 · 병합</b>
                        <small>잘못 나뉜 도형만 보정</small>
                    </span>
                    <span class="stage3-step__status">대기</span>
                </button>

                <div class="stage3-step__body">
                    <div class="stage3-card">
                        <p class="stage3-help">
                            도면이나 우측 목록에서 구역을 선택합니다. Shift/Ctrl 클릭은 다중 선택입니다.
                            드래그 수동 추가와 병합은 구역을 나누는 용도만 사용합니다.
                        </p>

                        <button type="button" class="stage3-btn stage3-btn--dark" id="manualAddBtn">수동 구역 추가</button>
                        <button type="button" class="stage3-btn" id="cancelToolBtn">선택/도구 해제</button>
                        <button type="button" class="stage3-btn stage3-btn--green" id="mergeSectionsBtn">선택 구역 병합</button>
                        <button type="button" class="stage3-btn stage3-btn--red" id="deleteSectionsBtn">선택 구역 삭제</button>

                        <div class="stage3-selection-summary" id="selectionSummary">선택 구역 없음</div>
                        <button type="button" class="stage3-btn stage3-btn--primary" id="goPart3Btn">다음: 그룹/번호 지정</button>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>

            <section class="stage3-step" id="part3Panel" data-step="3">
                <button type="button" class="stage3-step__header" id="partBtn3">
                    <span class="stage3-step__num">3</span>
                    <span class="stage3-step__text">
                        <b>그룹 확정</b>
                        <small>A~Z 그룹 + 그룹별 번호</small>
                    </span>
                    <span class="stage3-step__status">대기</span>
                </button>

                <div class="stage3-step__body">
                    <div class="stage3-card stage3-card--compact">
                        <p class="stage3-help stage3-help--compact">
                            색상별로 자동 묶고, 틀린 구역만 선택해서 그룹을 바꾸면 됩니다. 저장은 상단 헤더의 <b>저장하기</b> 버튼을 사용합니다.
                        </p>

                        <div class="stage3-quick-panel">
                            <div class="stage3-quick-panel__title">자동 그룹화</div>
                            <div class="stage3-compact-actions stage3-compact-actions--three">
                                <label class="stage3-mini-field" for="groupTolerance">
                                    <span>색상 허용</span>
                                    <input type="number" id="groupTolerance" value="42" min="1" max="180">
                                </label>
                                <button type="button" class="stage3-btn stage3-btn--green" id="autoGroupBtn">색상별 자동 그룹화</button>
                                <button type="button" class="stage3-btn stage3-btn--dark" id="renumberGroupsBtn">번호 재정렬</button>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <div class="stage3-quick-panel">
                            <div class="stage3-quick-panel__title">선택 구역 수정</div>
                            <div class="stage3-compact-actions stage3-compact-actions--three">
                                <label class="stage3-mini-field" for="groupKeyInput">
                                    <span>그룹</span>
                                    <input type="text" id="groupKeyInput" value="A" maxlength="2" placeholder="A">
                                </label>
                                <label class="stage3-mini-field" for="groupIndexInput">
                                    <span>번호</span>
                                    <input type="number" id="groupIndexInput" value="1" min="1">
                                </label>
                                <label class="stage3-mini-field" for="sectionColorInput">
                                    <span>색상</span>
                                    <input type="color" id="sectionColorInput" value="#d9d9d9">
                                </label>
                            </div>
                            <div class="stage3-compact-actions stage3-compact-actions--two">
                                <label class="stage3-mini-field" for="sectionNameInput">
                                    <span>최종명</span>
                                    <input type="text" id="sectionNameInput" placeholder="A1" readonly>
                                </label>
                                <button type="button" class="stage3-btn stage3-btn--dark" id="applyInfoBtn">선택 구역 적용</button>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <div class="stage3-quick-panel">
                            <div class="stage3-quick-panel__title">그룹 단체 수정</div>
                            <div class="stage3-compact-actions stage3-compact-actions--three">
                                <select id="groupBatchSelect" title="수정할 그룹"></select>
                                <input type="text" id="groupRenameInput" maxlength="2" placeholder="그룹명 변경">
                                <button type="button" class="stage3-btn stage3-btn--green" id="applyGroupBatchBtn">그룹 전체 적용</button>
                            </div>
                            <div class="stage3-compact-actions stage3-compact-actions--two">
                                <button type="button" class="stage3-btn" id="selectGroupBtn">이 그룹 전체 선택</button>
                                <button type="button" class="stage3-btn stage3-btn--green" id="autoNameBtn">그룹별 번호 정리</button>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <details class="stage3-advanced-box">
                            <summary>고급 설정 / 수동 일괄 입력</summary>
                            <div class="stage3-advanced-box__body">
                                <div class="stage3-form-grid stage3-form-grid--two stage3-form-grid--compact">
                                    <div>
                                        <label for="labelInput">표시 라벨</label>
                                        <input type="text" id="labelInput" placeholder="비우면 구역명 표시">
                                    </div>
                                    <div>
                                        <label for="floorInput">선택 구역 층</label>
                                        <input type="text" id="floorInput" value="1">
                                    </div>
                                    <div>
                                        <label for="gradeInput">선택 구역 등급</label>
                                        <input type="text" id="gradeInput" value="일반석">
                                    </div>
                                    <div>
                                        <label for="priceInput">선택 구역 가격</label>
                                        <input type="number" id="priceInput" value="132000" min="0">
                                    </div>
                                    <div>
                                        <label for="groupColorInput">그룹 색상</label>
                                        <input type="color" id="groupColorInput" value="#d9d9d9" title="그룹 색상">
                                    </div>
                                    <div>
                                        <label for="groupFloorInput">그룹 층</label>
                                        <input type="text" id="groupFloorInput" value="1" placeholder="층">
                                    </div>
                                    <div>
                                        <label for="groupGradeInput">그룹 등급</label>
                                        <input type="text" id="groupGradeInput" value="일반석" placeholder="등급">
                                    </div>
                                    <div>
                                        <label for="groupPriceInput">그룹 가격</label>
                                        <input type="number" id="groupPriceInput" value="132000" min="0" placeholder="가격">
                                    </div>
                                </div>

                                <div class="stage3-bulk-name-box stage3-bulk-name-box--compact">
                                    <label for="nameBatchInput">구역 그룹 수동 입력</label>
                                    <textarea id="nameBatchInput" rows="4" placeholder="A\nA\nA\nB\nB 또는 A1, A2처럼 직접 입력"></textarea>
                                    <div class="stage3-inline-actions">
                                        <button type="button" class="stage3-btn stage3-btn--dark" id="sampleNameTemplateBtn">A/B/C 예시</button>
                                        <button type="button" class="stage3-btn stage3-btn--green" id="applyNameBatchBtn">정렬 순서대로 적용</button>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </details>

                        <button type="button" class="stage3-btn stage3-btn--primary" id="toStage4Btn">Stage 4 좌석 배치로 이동</button>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>

        </div>
    </aside>

    <main class="seatmap-main stage3-main">
        <div class="stage3-canvas-toolbar">
            <strong id="canvasTitle">구역 그룹화 도면</strong>
            <span id="canvasSize">-</span>
            <span id="canvasGuide">색상 자동 그룹화 후 틀린 구역만 선택해서 수정하세요.</span>
        </div>

        <div class="stage3-canvas-scroll" id="canvasScroll">
            <div class="stage3-canvas-box" id="canvasBox">
                <canvas class="stage3-canvas-base" id="canvas"></canvas>
                <canvas class="stage3-canvas-overlay" id="overlay"></canvas>
            </div>
        </div>
    </main>

    <aside class="seatmap-side seatmap-side--right stage3-right">
        <div class="stage3-side-card">
            <h3>원본 미니맵</h3>
            <img id="miniImg" alt="Stage 3 원본 미니맵">
            <p class="stage3-help stage3-help--small">cropped-image.png 또는 seatmap-image.png 확인용입니다.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="stage3-side-card">
            <h3>선택 정보</h3>
            <div class="stage3-info-grid">
                <div><b id="totalCount">0</b><span>전체 구역</span></div>
                <div><b id="selectedCount">0</b><span>선택 구역</span></div>
                <div><b id="selectedArea">-</b><span>면적</span></div>
                <div><b id="selectedName">-</b><span>그룹/구역명</span></div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="stage3-side-card">
            <div class="stage3-side-head">
                <h3>그룹별 구역 목록</h3>
                <button type="button" class="stage3-text-btn" id="sortSectionsBtn">정렬</button>
            </div>
            <div class="stage3-section-list" id="sectionList">
                <div class="stage3-empty">아직 구역이 없습니다.</div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="stage3-side-card">
            <h3>결과 미리보기</h3>
            <canvas id="previewCanvas"></canvas>
            <p class="stage3-help stage3-help--small">흰 글자 라벨이 표시된 검수용 debug-polygons.png로 저장됩니다.</p>
        </div>
    </aside>

    <div class="seatmap-toast" id="toast"></div>
</div>
